  "summary": "The Dashboard presents a personalized overview containing a Timeline of upcoming activities and deadlines and a Calendar with month navigation and course filtering.",
  "where_it_fits": "Accessible from the top navigation bar via the Dashboard link, this module is the user's landing/overview page that aggregates information across My Courses and links into course-level views (e.g., Course Page and full calendar). It sits early in the user session lifecycle as the central hub users consult after signing in.",
